'''compLexity.Red''' was a League of Legends team under the '''compLexity''' organization, the sister team of '''[[compLexity.Black]]'''.

== History ==
On February 4, 2014 compLexity picks up the roster of [[Skyline]] to form '''compLexity.Red'''. They competed in Riot's [[2014 NA Challenger Series]], placing 3rd in the [[2014 NA Challenger Series/Spring/Series 1|Spring Series #1]], 5th-8th in the [[2014 NA Challenger Series/Spring/Series 2|Spring Series #2]], and then 5th/6th in the [[2014 NA Challenger Series/Spring/Playoffs|spring playoffs]]. Shortly after the playoffs, the team disbanded, and their sister team [[compLexity.Black]] became the flagship team [[compLexity]].

